items.title: Awesome Qubes OS
items.content_text:
### Kernels / Crypto

*   [eBPF](https://ebpf.io) - eBPF is a revolutionary technology with origins in the Linux kernel that can run sandboxed programs in an operating system kernel.

### Exploitation Tools / Unikernel-like

*   [MemProcFS (⭐3.7k)](https://github.com/ufrisk/MemProcFS) - MemProcFS is an easy and convenient way of viewing physical memory as files in a virtual file system.
    *   [MemProcFS-Plugins (⭐57)](https://github.com/ufrisk/MemProcFS-plugins) - This repository contains various non-core plugins for MemProcFS - The Memory Process File System.
